{
  "stem": "11144.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And that was in 1945.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It had to be in the summer of 1945, when they started to have transports out of the-- when-- when there was the pact between Germany and Russia.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And Germany was giving up their terrains on the west part of Poland, and they took the terrains on the eastern part of Poland, like Lvov and all the thing.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The Russians started to have transports of-- whoever wanted to immigrate to-- you know, out of there to Poland, they could.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we hopped on one of those transports and got to Lodz, not having any idea of what's going-- of what we are going to find or whatever.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And while on this one, we got off the train.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the ride took two weeks to get back, two weeks in-- this was in cattle-- in cattle trains that we were going.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And when my mother got off the train, all of a sudden, she met somebody.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "She says, oh, do you know that your-- your husband's sister is-- lives-- lived through the war, is in Lodz right now, and she is there with her two daughters.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So that's how we reunited with part of the family, stayed in Lodz for about half a year.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And my stepfather at that time started looking for something to do.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And Lodz was a little hard to get into, you know, to get a job or practice or whatever.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So everybody was going, again, west, to the Western parts-- the Western part that was German before.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So the two of them went and ended up in Legnica, found an apartment there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And people just came in and took apartments.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were throwing out the Germans, taking everything, whatever was the Germans', and you just settled down.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That's it.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
